```

### 12. Update the Home page

Replace the content of `ShipmentTracker.Client/Pages/Home.razor` with:
```razor
@page "/"

<PageTitle>ShipmentTracker - Logistics</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">ShipmentTracker</h1>
    <p class="lead">Real-time logistics tracking for dispatchers and customers.</p>
    <hr class="my-4" />
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
