## Important Notes
- The `.Client` project must have a project reference to nothing server-specific. The server project already references the client project.
- Do NOT add `@rendermode` to pages — it's global Auto.
- Make sure the `ShipmentTracker.Client.csproj` has `Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.WebAssembly` package reference (it should from the template).
- The `ShipmentTracker.csproj` (server) should already reference `Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Sqlite`.
